These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
City: prague, edinburgh, new-york, hannover
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, collecting, video-games, magic-tricks
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, 7up, iced-tea
There 4 different types of food: garlic, peas, eggplant, kiwi
1. the person drinking fanta is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person drinking 7up is between the person traveling to new-york and the person traveling to hannover##2
3. the person drinking fanta is the person eating garlic##1
4. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
6. the person eating eggplant is the person traveling to new-york##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
8. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| City   | edinburgh | hannover   | prague  | new-york  |
| Hobby   | collecting    | magic-tricks    | hiking      | video-games    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | fanta | 7up | milk |
| Food     | kiwi  | garlic       | peas    | eggplant     |

