.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, cola, coffee
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, folk, funk, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, italian, spanish, pakistani
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, chestnut, grey, green
1. the person who likes green is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
3. the pakistani is the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the fan trance is between the spanish and the person who likes apricot##2
6. the person who likes green is between the fan trance and the pakistani##2
7. the canadian is on the far right##1
8. the fan folk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
9. the fan funk is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage         | coffee | fanta    | cola  | milk    |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | folk  | trance  | funk |
| Nationality           | pakistani      | spanish       | italian      | canadian       |
| Color         | chestnut    | green | grey | apricot |

