.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
House: futuristic, wooden, gothic-revival, ranch-style
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, december, may, february
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, rose, aconite, lily
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, light-blue, fuchsia, mauve
1. the person who growsaconite is the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who growslily##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person who growsrose is the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the futuristic house is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in february##2
9. the person who's birthday is in may is between the gothic-revival house and the person who growsrose##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| House        | wooden | gothic-revival     | futuristic   | ranch-style     |
| Birthday       | december   | august   | may | february |
| Flower         | orchid   | aconite | lily       | rose    |
| Color   | fuchsia    | light-blue | ivory  | mauve    |

