 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person traveling to boston and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
