4 different pets are kept: fish, mouse, ferret, rat
1. the person who growslily is between the owner of the rat and the person who growsaconite##2
2. the person eating tomato is between the person who growslily and the person traveling to prague##2
3. the person traveling to boston is between the owner of the mouse and the person traveling to berlin##2
4. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
5. the person traveling to boston is the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
7. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
8. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
9. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
