 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who likes red and the person eating banana##2
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person eating carrot##1
 5. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 7. the person who likes pink is the person eating pepper##1
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
10. the person who likes red is the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Pet   | bird | dog | hedgehog  | horse  |
| Hobby   | video-games       | dancing   | fishing | puzzles    |
| Color   | pink   | red   | emerald | orange |
| Food     | pepper    | carrot   | strawberry    | banana  |

